  <body>
    <br><br><br>
        <head>
            <meta charset="utf-8">
            <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
            <title>BAC Calculator</title>
            <meta name="description" content="A calculator designed to estimate your blood alcohol content given the number and types of drinks consumed.">
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="main.css">
        </head>
            <h1>BAC Calculator</h1>
            <p>USE THIS BAC CALCULATOR TO FIND YOUR SWEET SPOT. FOR A SAFE NIGHT OF DRINKING, STAY AT A LEVEL OF 0.05 OR BELOW, AND IT'LL BE THE PERFECT BUZZ.</p>
            <br>
            <p>Please use the following chart to estimate the quantity of standard drinks consumed, each representing a single standard drink:</p>
            <a href="https://i.imgur.com/sAZ5xBY.jpg"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/sAZ5xBY.jpg" alt="Buzz'd" class: "center" "title="source: imgur.com" class="center" /></a>
            <form>
                Gender: <br>
                <select id="gender">
                    <option value="female">Female</option>
                    <option value="male">Male</option>
                    <option value="neither">Other</option>
                </select>
                <br><br> Weight: <br>
                <input type="number" id="weight" value="140"> lbs
                <br><br>Number of standard drinks:<br>
                <input type="number" id="drink_count" value="0">
                <br><br>Amount of time elapsed:<br>
                <input type="number" id="time_elapsed" value="0"> hours<br><br>
                <input type="button" id="go" value="Submit" onclick="calculateBAC();"/><br>
            </form>

            <script src="calculations.js"></script>
            <br><br><br>
        </body>



